My children's children are gonna fight cancer because of uranium pollution, how did they deserve that? ...and it is the same for all Balkan people no matter the nationality, so who was defending who there??? World health organization made a study on the consequences of nuclear pollution on public health, and made a conclusion that there are non!!!  ...am I supposed to trust them now? The only real victory for the Balkan people would be to unite in a lawsuit against NATO. 
       People are getting divided... Who is oppressing who here? Isn't that a little bit crazy when you think about it? "Hold him down while I inject him!!". Doesn't that sound the alarm? I would not call all this a vax and anti-vax division, but a division between oblivious, brainwashed zombi envy cowards on one side and people that can still think and stand up for themselves on the other. Where are you standing??? It is a troublesome time so where is the real debate?
